{"tid":1711974,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"斬首行動！！全人類注意：而家進攻特首辦！！","createTime":"2019-11-12T13:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:10:17.000Z","uid":200651,"like":38,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"73a65134b7ea2a1eb6221f1cbc465d8e16c4f285","tid":1711974,"uid":200651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"同我睇曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n孫子兵法 第十一卷 九地篇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">&ldquo;投之死地而後存，陷之亡地而後生&rdquo;</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n而家中大就係佢地嘅屋企，後無退路，必然固守。佢地知自己必定會死，所以唔會怕同popo開戰。<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n但正正係咁，先至真係要popo將注意力放喺中大，大家唔好擔心，佢地會守住。真係幫佢地就一定要直搗黃龍，一舉癱瘓敵人嘅指揮機制。趁敵後空虛，<strong>一舉攻下特首辦</strong>，擒賊擒王，敵人就會潰散。佢地知道有人保佢地先會咁囂張，一失去指揮，必定進退失據。<br />\n<br />\n再由中大突圍而出，合軍聚眾，<strong>動如雷震</strong> ，俘虜幾十個popo。<strong>優待一部分自願投降戰俘，同時逼迫反抗嘅popo。其餘popo嘅心理防禦會即時瓦解。咁樣警隊就會潰散</strong><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n最後，光復香港，時代革命！五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"bd75ac298e3066f16e48cde921017cb1af22eb48","tid":1711974,"uid":60868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"777係會展wo"},{"pid":"7fb97897298616dd626e68eefc126b21dd372925","tid":1711974,"uid":200651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:08:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fbfe5d04301a819dbc8c8b9bc1bc70f0ce385cc","tid":1711974,"uid":200651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c29a8085b1f84ce29e5ef245e6f40d8752cc82d","tid":1711974,"uid":227441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:09:24.000Z","msg":"去會展 斬首"},{"pid":"aa7a35e7b642f05775d7b982fa4f3d2fd28175c0","tid":1711974,"uid":200651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:09:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aaee8497b61d39d60fc395d0b4013fc178ee0d82","tid":1711974,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike"